{"tid":1506601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依個「反送中」同「佔中」運動嘅分別，無乜人講過","createTime":"2019-08-26T00:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T15:18:16.000Z","uid":8465,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f43e16ecdcf59b7ff67fa2e579404ce30042e3f9","tid":1506601,"uid":8465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:32:18.000Z","msg":"當年佔中，因為有大台，各政治團體都伸隻腳入去<br />\n搞搞下局外人根本唔知發展成點<br />\n慢慢大眾跟唔到成個走態<br />\n人心就散<br />\n<br />\n今次唔同係成個運動好簡單<br />\n就係示威、佔路、衝突<br />\n無將運動覆雜化<br />\n局外人跟到<br />\n人心不散"},{"pid":"518fda96f0974d79120ac83b0fb9bb566bf5bc80","tid":1506601,"uid":305009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:33:16.000Z","msg":"複雜化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外上次不斷割搞到嗰蓆勁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3286644a4fd775ee12fdf5656099e083413b4d","tid":1506601,"uid":9356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:33:37.000Z","msg":"我都覺得呢樣好重要<br />\n好多都唔明我地吸收左上次教訓<br />\n今次進步左好多<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"8f5f28a148b102972899bc23580b434507440f06","tid":1506601,"uid":9356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:35:56.000Z","msg":"同埋想講既係<br />\n今次真係引發左好大迴響<br />\n無論民意<br />\n國際關注都同佔中果次都冇得比<br />\n<br />\n我地要繼續向呢2方面邁進"},{"pid":"d25594e9395a875fc546658fa45507401d0ce998","tid":1506601,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:57:35.000Z","msg":"「圖」多個內地日文Twitter帳號惡意抹黑示威 並大量宣傳解放軍資訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b6360f4c82264b83947d1b1f14fe7e8812813a06","tid":1506601,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HgaPwE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HgaPwE.png&h=4b166d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jw3c5er.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJw3c5er.jpg&h=dd6decd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88a87de1fb2a8400d165861b7ef42464a1dd3cbf","tid":1506601,"uid":271250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"我認為最主要分別係根本。佔中原因係無雙普選加689放tear gas。無普選係屬於「無進步」；相反，送中係屬於「退步」。心理學上，失去d野既感覺比攞到d野強烈得多。<br />\n<br />\nBtw ,唔應該叫送中，要叫送共"}]}